{"tid":2152490,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ITZY 《Not Shy》比《WANNABE》難2.5倍”","createTime":"2020-08-12T04:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T08:12:22.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f092cda94fcf9ec168e15de191c9d84b9a82e9","tid":2152490,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"【newsen】ITZY 《Not Shy》MV預告公開&ldquo;編舞比《WANNABE》難2.5倍&rdquo;<br />\nITZY於12日通過官方SNS頻道公開的迷你3輯《Not Shy》同名主打曲MV預告視頻展現了獨一無二的舞蹈線條，再次證明了&ldquo;舞台匠人&rdquo;的面貌。成員們表示：&ldquo;新曲編舞比前作《WANNABE》難2.5倍，在快節奏beat上五個人都要一起配合細節。樸軫永超話PD說這是他這段時間看過的女團表演中最棒的，是歷代級的表演。希望粉絲們從頭到尾看完後都能發出'哇'的聲音&rdquo;。據悉《Not Shy》MV共進行了5天的拍攝，為了高完成度費了很多功夫。她們將通過MV展現魅力無限的視覺效果和夢幻般表情演技以及ITZY特有的壓倒性刀群舞等。<br />\n另外，ITZY新專將於17日下午5時通過各大音源網站公開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEunfKy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEunfKy.gif&h=9e062621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztkxCXT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FztkxCXT.gif&h=0e33931d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRTOVKz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRTOVKz.gif&h=2063e6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACUVAKz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACUVAKz.gif&h=c4619815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVczRhU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVczRhU.gif&h=cab40f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/675aa51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F675aa51.jpg&h=7294e171&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c196bc009d4d7609d362dd73c733e2d7da5fd00","tid":2152490,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"我愛柳真"},{"pid":"d649c32e166c0fc572b607a6d3198512ce3f0613","tid":2152490,"uid":266467,"l